        </item>
        <item>
            <title>iOS 17.2 推出日記新功能　記錄用家生活點滴</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/12/ios17-2-journal/news/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ios17-2-journal</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/12/ios17-2-journal/news/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 06:11:03 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[作者忘記分類]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1210017</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Apple 剛推出 iOS 17.2 更新，新功能「日記（Journal）」將在今月 12 日正式推出。除了常規更新外，可能讓人感到興趣的日記功能，可讓用家隨時記錄靈感隨想和生活點滴。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1210018 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Apple-Journal-app-2-up_big.jpg.large_2x-694x496.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="496" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Apple-Journal-app-2-up_big.jpg.large_2x-694x496.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Apple-Journal-app-2-up_big.jpg.large_2x-1260x900.jpg 1260w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Apple-Journal-app-2-up_big.jpg.large_2x-768x549.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Apple-Journal-app-2-up_big.jpg.large_2x-1536x1097.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Apple-Journal-app-2-up_big.jpg.large_2x.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲新功能「日記（Journal）」將在今月 12 日正式推出</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Apple 官方希望推出「日記」應用程式，可助用家撰寫日記反思及記下感恩之事，促進身心健康。「日記」應用程式用家可捕捉及記錄日常點滴和人生特別時刻，亦可附上相片、影片、錄音、地點等。 用家可以在「日記」應用程式中加入來自其他應用程式的新聞文章、音樂、或 podcast。用家可瀏覽過去的日記紀錄、加入書籤，或按相片、體能訓練、地點等等篩選檢視。「編排通知」可助用戶培養寫日記習慣。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1210019 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Apple-Journal-app-personalized-suggestions_inline.jpg.large_2x-414x580.jpg" alt="" width="414" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Apple-Journal-app-personalized-suggestions_inline.jpg.large_2x-414x580.jpg 414w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Apple-Journal-app-personalized-suggestions_inline.jpg.large_2x-643x900.jpg 643w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Apple-Journal-app-personalized-suggestions_inline.jpg.large_2x-768x1075.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Apple-Journal-app-personalized-suggestions_inline.jpg.large_2x-1097x1536.jpg 1097w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Apple-Journal-app-personalized-suggestions_inline.jpg.large_2x.jpg 1143w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 414px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲用家可以在「日記」應用程式中加入來自其他應用程式的新聞文章、音樂、或 podcast</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">全新 Journaling Suggestions API 等第三方日記應用程式亦可為用家日記可紀錄的時刻。 「日記」及 Journaling Suggestions API 隨 iOS 17.2 同時推出。</p><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://www.apple.com/hk/newsroom/2023/12/apple-launches-journal-app-a-new-app-for-reflecting-on-everyday-moments/">Apple</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/12/ios17-2-journal/news/">iOS 17.2 推出日記新功能　記錄用家生活點滴</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/12/ios17-2-journal/news/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
