            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[電動車]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1209961</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>中國品牌的電動車在香港日漸普及，其中上汽大通旗下的 Maxus 也憑 MIFA 9 打入香港市場，最近更引入新的 MIFA 7，尺寸細一圈與香港需求頗大的中型 MPV 接近。<br /><span id="more-1209961"></span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/409827233_761013032711267_2170033124724170342_n.jpg" alt="" width="2048" height="1365" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1209962" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/409827233_761013032711267_2170033124724170342_n.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/409827233_761013032711267_2170033124724170342_n-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/409827233_761013032711267_2170033124724170342_n-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/409827233_761013032711267_2170033124724170342_n-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/409827233_761013032711267_2170033124724170342_n-1536x1024.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p>上汽大通旗下的 Maxus 最近在香港正式推出 MIFA 7，長闊高分別為 4,907 x 1,885 x 1,768 毫米，接近香港流行的家庭 MPV 例如 Honda Stepwgn 和 Toyota Noah 等，低於 1.8 米的車高也適合大部分停車場。配備上 MIFA 7 也算破壞找到，加入了特大天窗和 12.3 吋數碼儀錶板，以及多項主動式智能安全配備，在市區比較狹窄的馬路和車位上都能夠更易操控。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/409179279_761013042711266_1724647761009246340_n.jpg" alt="" width="2048" height="1365" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1209963" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/409179279_761013042711266_1724647761009246340_n.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/409179279_761013042711266_1724647761009246340_n-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/409179279_761013042711266_1724647761009246340_n-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/409179279_761013042711266_1724647761009246340_n-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/409179279_761013042711266_1724647761009246340_n-1536x1024.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p>至於大家都很在意的續航力方面，兩款 77 kWh 和 90 kWh 電池可以分別提供 527 公里和 605 公里的續航力，馬力有 244 匹，可以應付一般日常駕駛。MIFA 7「一換一」價錢為 HK$399,000，價格包含英之傑原廠維修以及 8 年／200,000 公里（以先到者為準）電池保養。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/409751757_761013116044592_2655889195001919891_n.jpg" alt="" width="2048" height="1365" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1209964" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/409751757_761013116044592_2655889195001919891_n.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/409751757_761013116044592_2655889195001919891_n-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/409751757_761013116044592_2655889195001919891_n-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/409751757_761013116044592_2655889195001919891_n-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/409751757_761013116044592_2655889195001919891_n-1536x1024.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p>來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/HongKongMaxus/">Maxus Hong Kong</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/11/maxus-mifa-7/life-tech/auto/">上汽大通 Maxus MIFA 7 40 萬有找　 5 米長車身搶中型 MPV 市場</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
